[
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_52_0",
    "text": "1992年6月，《21世纪议程》.破坏环境一可持续发展",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.16271501627150162,
      0.14544257979598552,
      0.7271036727103672,
      0.16847647252385653
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_52",
    "order": 1
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_52_1",
    "text": "4.城市化问题",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11622501162250116,
      0.20993747943402435,
      0.27615062761506276,
      0.23099703849950642
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_52",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_52_2",
    "text": "(1)人口和城市的分布",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.14783821478382148,
      0.24086870681145114,
      0.3774988377498838,
      0.26390259953932216
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_52",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_52_3",
    "text": "①特点：人口分布极不平衡，90%的人口居生在东部沿海地带，而且大城市十分 集中。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1097164109716411,
      0.27179993418887793,
      0.9390980939098094,
      0.32379072063178677
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_52",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_52_4",
    "text": "②带来许多“城市病：资源紧缺、交通拥挤、住房困难、就业紧张、污染严重犯。 罪增多.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10599721059972106,
      0.3343205001645278,
      0.9409576940957695,
      0.38565317538664035
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_52",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_52_5",
    "text": "③解决措施：进行合理的城市规划、建立卫星城：城市中工业和人口向郊区分 散：加强城市管理.重视保护和治理城市环境。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10134821013482101,
      0.397499177360974,
      0.9502556950255695,
      0.4501480750246792
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_52",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_52_6",
    "text": "(2)主要城市：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1515574151557415,
      0.4600197433366239,
      0.2780102278010228,
      0.48042119118130966
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_52",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_52_7",
    "text": "圣保罗：经济中心.最大的城市和工业中心 里约热内户：商业和金融中心，第二大城市. 巴西利亚：政治中心、首都.是新建城市.",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1803812180381218,
      0.4889766370516617,
      0.5913528591352859,
      0.5745310957551826
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_52",
    "order": 8
  },
